Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是吠陀的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格…不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的計劃本身的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎  李本茲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯納家為了這一刻已經等了200多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  用吠陀把攻擊Trinity的部隊的圖像調出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  從這裡把那資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在屏蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下載完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是擬太陽爐搭載型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰火正在擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:20.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,0)}非洲大陸  西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  還沒和拉古那取得聯絡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的新型號也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥  我們該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Level 5  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始Level 6的控制作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得無聊的話  看看這樣的情報怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈貝完成了GN-X的配置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  他的任務到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}聯合  高軌道空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你是Flag Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都不知道  你是在裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的王牌飛行員  帕特里克·克拉薩烏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉薩烏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  第一個被Gundam介入  被整得一塌糊塗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要翻我舊賬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  聯合的Top Gun在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡上級大尉不參加本次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被嚇成膽小鬼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合的王牌飛行員也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你誣衊我們隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反對暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聯合的達利爾·道奇準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的卡蒂·馬內金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責本次作戰的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  必將全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特里克  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有戰果的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  不飛Flag的意義就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒臉再見隊長了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這麼勉強你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是任務嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統的構築狀態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成八成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吠陀對Gundam的輔助切斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師的負擔會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近變得柔和了哦  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傾向  好傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  拜託你們了  再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從情報來看  吠陀的系統被什麼人利用這點可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:07:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在沒有吠陀的情況下與同型機對抗  能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩心的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有吠陀的輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有Gundam和皇小姐的戰術預報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不知道吧  她過去曾犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都會犯錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或許曾犯下了非常大的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她為了償還過去才選擇了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用酒精平息受創傷的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這點的  也只有人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  洛克恩  我的事情你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位  皇小姐指示要我們到貨櫃待機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞  我只說一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為現在狀況正在惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4部Gundam的配合才更為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這些話對刹那·F·清榮去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾…
